{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_02_01",
  "title": "サニーピース 02 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに実家に帰省したのに\nどうしてすずと芽衣までついて来てるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came home to visit after so long‚\nbut why are Suzu and Mei here too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.4671431541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.6666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんとご両親の許可はいただいているのですから\n別に構わないでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have your parents' permission‚\nso there's no problem‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6666667938,
      "endTime": 11.6270748138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.7666664759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "いつの間にうちの親と連絡先交換したのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When did you exchange number with my parents…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7666664759,
      "endTime": 15.766666666699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0000003814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのお母さんがライブに来てくれた時に\n連絡先教えてーってお願いしたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Rei-chan's mom came to our live‚\nI asked her for her contact info.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.0000003814,
      "endTime": 22.2842165946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は物怖じってものを知らないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have no sense of boundaries‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4999989826,
      "endTime": 25.737572653900003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.933332316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、すずにゃんが\n「怜を一人で実家に帰すのは心配ですわ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Suzu-nyan said‚\n\"I'm worried about letting Rei go home alone.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.933332316,
      "endTime": 31.4338990846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "「私達もついて行って\n何かあったら怜の味方をしますわよ」って言って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"We'll go with you‚\nand if anything happens‚ we'll be on Rei's side.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.633332316,
      "endTime": 38.3703845659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5666656493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことは言わなくていいのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't have to say that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5666656493,
      "endTime": 41.8117449759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……仕方ないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… It can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9999989826,
      "endTime": 45.453604443699994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.6666656493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ、そういえば怜ちゃんの部屋ってどこ？\n怜ちゃんの部屋、見てみたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ by the way‚ which room is Rei-chan's?\nI want to see Rei-chan's room~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6666656493,
      "endTime": 53.1469377517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.333332316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "もう。芽衣は遠慮ってものを知らないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ you have no sense of restraint‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.333332316,
      "endTime": 57.470135037000006,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5800.000063599995,
          "startTime": 59.1333323796
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.334860999993,
          "startTime": 58.866667177
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7600.005340699994,
          "startTime": 60.9333376567
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 58.5999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 58.5999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 60.3000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ここが怜ちゃんの部屋なんだ～。あっ、トロフィー！\nこれってダンス大会で優勝した時の？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is Rei-chan's room~. Ah‚ a trophy!\nIs this from when you won that dance competition?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8333412171,
      "endTime": 70.992344284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 65.6000091553
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 71.2000091553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど……恥ずかしいから\nあまりジロジロ見ないでよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but… it's embarrassing‚\nso don't stare at it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2000091553,
      "endTime": 76.84613142010001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 77.0333424886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "コルクボードに写真が沢山貼ってありますわね\nこれは家族写真かしら、怜が子供の頃の写真ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a lot of photos on this corkboard.\nAre these family photos? Photos of Rei from when she was little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333424886,
      "endTime": 85.9563130696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "これは小学校の運動会で、こっちはテーマパークで\nキャストさんと撮った記念写真だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one is from your elementary school sports day‚\nand this one is a photo you took with cast members at a theme park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.166675822,
      "endTime": 92.5959954898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ちっちゃい怜がダンススタジオで踊ってる写真も\nありますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's also a photo of\nlittle Rei dancing in a dance studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8000091553,
      "endTime": 97.2462450981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 97.4333424886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに小さい頃からダンスをやってたんだね～\n怜ちゃんは何がきっかけでダンスを始めたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been dancing since you were that young~?\nWhat made you start dancing‚ Rei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4333424886,
      "endTime": 105.895746549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 102.1333424886
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 106.0666763306
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "大した話じゃないわ。私が小学生の時に\n家族でテーマパークへ遊びに行ったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a big deal. When I was in elementary school‚\nmy family went to a theme park…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666763306,
      "endTime": 113.7647943497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "そこで着ぐるみのキャラクターと大勢のキャストが\nステージで踊っているのを見たのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And there‚ I saw a bunch of people in mascot costumes\nand cast members dancing on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9666763306,
      "endTime": 119.6876286507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 119.9000096639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "そのパレードが、まるで夢の中にいるみたいに楽しくて\nダンスはこんなにも人を魅了するんだって感動したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The parade was so much fun‚ it felt like I was in a dream‚\nand I was moved by how captivating dance could be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9000096639,
      "endTime": 128.8059275945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "その時に思ったのよ。私もこんな風に踊ってみたい\nダンスでみんなに夢を届けたいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that moment‚ I thought‚ \"I want to dance like that too.\"\n\"I want to bring dreams to everyone through dance…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0000096639,
      "endTime": 138.8338441213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 139.0333450318
    },
