      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-reibro004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は父さんの言いなりにはならない\nバンドで成功して、実力で父さんを黙らせてやる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not going to do what he says.\nI'm going to make it big with the band‚ and prove him wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.7999944053,
      "endTime": 292.9866449676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 293.3999903363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei's",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-reibro005.m4a",
      "text": "だからもう家でギターは弾けないけど\n怜は俺のことを応援してくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I can't play guitar at home anymore‚\nbut will you support me‚ Rei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.3999903363,
      "endTime": 298.31999022179997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　私はお兄ちゃんを応援する\nだって私は、お兄ちゃんのファン第一号なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'll support you!\nBecause I'm your number one fan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.666685486,
      "endTime": 307.0413562777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 308.2000546775
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 308.2000546775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "結局、お兄さんはバンドを続けるために\n家を出たんですのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ in the end‚ your brother left home\nto pursue his band?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.3333277386,
      "endTime": 315.1489513081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 315.3333277386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。医大の受験に失敗して、内緒でバンド活動を\n続けていたことがばれて、お父さんと大喧嘩になったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. He failed his medical school entrance exams‚ and when Dad found out\nhe was still playing in the band secretly‚ they had a huge fight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.3333277386,
      "endTime": 324.6760943097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 325.7667213442
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 326.0333676658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-reidad001.m4a",
      "text": "東京でバンドをやりたいだと？\nバカも休み休み言え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to be in a band in Tokyo?\nDon't be ridiculous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.8666305544,
      "endTime": 332.7866244795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-reidad002.m4a",
      "text": "音楽で食べていけるのは才能のある一部の人間だけだ\nお前なんかがやっていける訳ないだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Only a handful of talented people can make a living from music.\nThere's no way you can make it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.0333440147,
      "endTime": 342.0666735968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-reidad003.m4a",
      "text": "もっと現実を見ろ、お前は医者になるんだ\n私はお前のためを思って言ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Face reality‚ you're going to be a doctor.\nI'm saying this for your own good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.3000656131,
      "endTime": 352.0400594715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 352.2333928429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "怜の兄",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei's",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-reibro006.m4a",
      "text": "父さんは俺に医者を継がせたいだけだろ\n俺は父さんの人形じゃない！　俺の人生は俺が決める！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just want me to inherit your practice!\nI'm not your puppet! I'll decide my own life!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.2333928429,
      "endTime": 359.8533806168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 360.9667701724
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 360.9667701724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "私は兄の夢を応援してたけど、父は理解してくれなくて\n大喧嘩の末に、兄は夢を掴むために家を出て行ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I supported my brother's dream‚ but my father wouldn't understand‚\nand after a big fight‚ he left home to chase his dream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 362.0667139693,
      "endTime": 373.6000069302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "兄に失望した父は、私に期待するようになった\n兄のかわりに私を医者にしようとした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Disappointed in my brother‚ Dad started putting his hopes on me.\nHe tried to make me a doctor instead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 373.9333704634,
      "endTime": 382.5145041152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichireiroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichireiroom",
      "startTime": 382.70003713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_02_01-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "そして私は、勉強の邪魔だからって理由で\nずっと続けていたダンスをやめさせられたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ he made me quit dancing‚\nwhich I had been doing for so long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.70003713,
      "endTime": 391.31341546410005,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}